yer","external":""},"html":"<p>Jazz is a powerful, elegant and free music player for Android following material UI guideliness from google .A clean music player with a customizable interface.\nGet it at <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=rubin.jazz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Play Store</a></p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Smart Pad - Note pad clone in java","tech":["Java","Swing"],"github":"https://github.com/rubiin/SmartPad","external":"https://github.com/rubiin/SmartPad"},"html":"<p>Smartpad or Jpad is a text editor based on java. I tried to clone notepad app on windows and added some extra featues.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Nest-pgpromise","tech":["Nestjs","Typescript","Postgres"],"github":"https://github.com/nest-pgpromise","external":"https://rubiin.vercel.app/nest-pgpromise"},"html":"<p>A Module for Utilizing Pg-promise with NestJS</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Dagr2.py","tech":["Python","Mechanical soup"],"github":"https://github.com/rubiin/dagr2","external":""},"html":"<p>dagr2.py (deviantArt gallery ripper) is a deviantArt image downloader script written in Python.\nIt can download every image (deviation) in a gallery, as well as every favorited deviation a deviant may have.\nOriginally developed at <a href=\"http://lovecastle.org/dagr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://lovecastle.org/dagr/</a> (now defunct), development now continues on <a href=\"https://github.com/rubiin/dagr2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github</a></p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Lappy ball","tech":["Android","Unity"],"github":"https://github.com/rubiin/Lappy-Ball","external":"https://github.com/rubiin/Lappy-Ball"},"html":"<p>Arcade game where you have to complete laps to score. Get it here <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rubin.dodger&#x26;hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Playstore</a>.</p>"}}]},"contact":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Get in touch"},"html":"<p>I love connecting with different people so if you want to say hi,I would love to hear about your project and big idea.</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["3115057458"],"slicesMap":{}}